Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:22.83,sign_477_1__I_might_be_movi,<-,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}I might be moving to Chiba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.37,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotarou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.51,Flashback,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you're moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:35.71,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.37,Flashback,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Where? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.72,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm looking up schools in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:43.34,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you heard of Koumei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.43,Flashback,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.43,Main,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Her grades are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.84,Main,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.57,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.26,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It must be difficult on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.31,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was due to her father's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.82,sign_4324_22_Koumei_Private_H,,0000,0000,0000,,Koumei Private High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.82,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried because \Nit's such a critical time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.83,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the application form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.90,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.85,sign_4900_26_Factoring,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Factoring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.34,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.19,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Your LINE message surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.80,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:47.96,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.28,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I had my parent-teacher meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.00,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to apply to Koumei \Nwith a recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.00,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.26,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.25,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.69,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.50,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.15,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine, even far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:32.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.50,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.54,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.66,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not on recommendation. \NJust general admission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.75,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.59,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really far, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.70,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it takes over two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.84,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I decided to go to your cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.20,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.12,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.64,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The Kawagoe Festival is this weekend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.27,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.39,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.26,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.38,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.71,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.96,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.04,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.30,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.41,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,They're really good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.74,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.27,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.10,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:33.74,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.59,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.54,sign_9633_64_Rock_Paper_Sciss,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-Paper-Scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.54,sign_9633_65_Win____earn_two,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Win -> Earn Two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.54,sign_9633_66_Lose_Draw____Ear,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lose/Draw -> Earn One
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.31,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.24,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.73,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.50,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's all go to the haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.93,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.86,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that for kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.71,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.37,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother trying to taunt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.27,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,That was so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.77,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made fun of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.78,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that was kind of awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.93,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:18.78,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.92,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one Kotarou-kun's been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.07,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was that Azumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.91,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,He looked really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.78,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.96,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.37,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.14,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty demanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:55.10,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, about our \Nlight novel discussion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.46,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.16,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should keep it as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.08,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.30,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,That novel you had me read before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.86,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,I think light novel fans \Nwould appreciate it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.47,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.87,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have some time until the next shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.52,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can go enjoy the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:16.88,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.33,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.35,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go relax?
