Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.51,sign_13865_107_Okay,->,0000,0000,0000,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.14,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.52,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Loser takes the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.02,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.04,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.20,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:50.99,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.27,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.26,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.69,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had imokoi in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.89,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.16,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.07,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want imokoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.47,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hungry?
