Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.84,sign_14760_127_I_m_with_the_tra,->,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the track club people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.99,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mizuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.66,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Want to get some imokoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.27,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.95,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.40,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.91,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.53,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.35,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Kawagoe specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.45,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to have \Nany once you move, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.48,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.93,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.81,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.63,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:12.03,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.55,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,When you told me you were moving, \NI didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.44,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:34.20,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I always saw you running so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:56.92,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, um... I'm in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.31,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.19,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,But... why Azumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.38,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I know you way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.63,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.44,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.12,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:20.42,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend, Hira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.27,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're important to me, \Nbut it's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.11,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.30,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.87,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.08,sign_18440_157_Come_to_Toki_no_,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Come to Toki no Kane
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.64,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.89,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd get to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:15.53,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I told everyone I was leaving early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.28,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.36,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Were you with Hira just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.59,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.17,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.77,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we lost a game and had \Nto throw away the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:28.99,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.87,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your dance, Kotarou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.17,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.08,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How long is your break?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.86,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,About an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.24,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.46,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.09,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll have imokoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.22,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.22,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all full.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.92,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kotarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.49,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.82,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.00,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.20,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have a girlfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.82,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.94,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, introduce us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.35,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.86,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Man, to be young...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.78,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.32,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.88,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Azumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.21,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.11,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.62,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.63,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.43,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.99,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.27,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.01,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about me moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:39.75,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.83,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,But what else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:41.56,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.12,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.09,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.95,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.03,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.32,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.17,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.17,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Another guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:12.96,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:22.72,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.27,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He confessed to me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.81,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I turned him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.87,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get you some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.11,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.39,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.66,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.45,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
