Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.08,sign_25544_217_Okay,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.08,sign_25544_218_I_ll_be_right_th,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there
