Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.82,sign_26299_221__I_might_be__mov,->,0000,0000,0000,,I might be \Nmoving to Chiba
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.53,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.34,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.20,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,I get sleepy whenever I try to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.93,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.21,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm like, "I'll just finish talking \Non LINE before I start studying..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.85,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,And then your parents go, "Start studying!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.62,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.28,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,It just makes you want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.46,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.34,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
