Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That changes the meaning, \Nso you need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.41,sign_28362_248_Koumei__High_Sch,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Koumei \NHigh School
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.98,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.25,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.48,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we had a request for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:30.43,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,They said they had a request for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:31.67,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.66,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.42,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.54,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even told my parents yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.69,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,They probably won't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.32,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:57.61,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell you after \NI talked to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.45,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.72,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,And writing and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:09.84,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,And I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.53,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.58,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.66,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:37.68,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.99,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.77,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:45.24,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you hated me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.22,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
