Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.66,Main,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking pictures for \Nthe graduation album.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:06.84,Main_Top,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew we had so many \Nmembers who don't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.35,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the literature club?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:11.81,Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:13.13,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...
